    "description": "<p>This spell reveals whether there is at least one trap within range and within line of sight. You don't learn the number, location, or kind of traps detected. For the purpose of this spell, a trap is a hidden mechanical device or magical effect which is designed to harm you or put you in danger, such as a pit trap, symbol spell, or alarm bell on a door, but not a natural hazard.</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p><strong>Rare: Reactive Find Traps.</strong> When you cast the spell, choose a point within 10 feet. The spell triggers 1d4 traps in a 5-foot radius around that point. </p><p></p>",
